Package org.hawaiiframework.async

Class HawaiiAsyncUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hawaiiframework.async.HawaiiAsyncUtil
  • public final class HawaiiAsyncUtil
extends Object
    Utility to retrieve the value from a CompletableFuture.

    All exceptions are wrapped in a HawaiiTaskExecutionException.
